{"tid":390294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有仔女既入] 邊套學前動畫/卡通片你會比小朋友睇?","createTime":"2017-09-07T03:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T08:00:20.000Z","uid":120750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d80ad6997e7c3526a82366c754f0eb61907106b8","tid":390294,"uid":120750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的 屋企有細路 一個就快5歲 另一個就3歲左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時無乜點理兩個靚仔靚妹睇咩電視或者卡通, 但係呢排發掘原來睇咩卡通係會好影響佢地扭計要買公仔/ 平時無聊時候既心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網做左D research 聽講話好既學前動畫片或者卡通片都可以比佢地打好D個底, 無論性格定基本認知能力<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家平時比你D小朋友睇咩卡通? 或者佢地呢個年紀 (2-5/6歲) 鍾意D咩人物? 我自己仲停留緊係比卡超 數碼暴龍 既年代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係呢D 都可能係小學之後先會睇既  如果for 早少少階段既小朋友 有乜推介?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時淨係識Peppa Pig 同咩 Dora &amp; Explorer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n受而家香港小朋友歡迎既有乜?  最好中性D啦因爲一仔一女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d37a67f547f8a1c6bc394b1e55a8a64a411c03","tid":390294,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:44:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"806b0d595788a7dcd83f3d8a7ebdb161667611bb","tid":390294,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:44:49.000Z","msg":"巧虎，學禮貌同品德幾好，但好洗腦"},{"pid":"adaf0b47e9a00be83d070ab3811948ddc6002277","tid":390294,"uid":120750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狂賭之淵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"